
EM-seq v2 FULL CHOREOGRAPHY, COLUMN 1, DRY
Reagent adds -> ODTC out/back (x8 programs) -> 3x magnet + SPRI cleanup out/back.
Every leg runs its own scoped script; geometry is not re-derived here.
STATUS: written, simulation-first, NOT yet run on hardware. Tune each leg before trusting it.

