Closing connection to USB device.
Initializing STAR with skip_autoload=True...
Tip behavior: discard_tips=False (production discards; --return-tips is dry-observe only).
Backend: STARBackend (REAL hardware - human-gated).
Assigning EM-seq post-ligation cleanup deck (1.1X): mag pos2 + trough pos3...
Using p50 filter tips resource factory: hamilton_96_tiprack_50uL_filter
Using p300 filter tips resource factory: hamilton_96_tiprack_300uL_filter

Deck:
  rail48 pos1 = p50 tips (elution add, residual ethanol removal)
  rail48 pos2 = p300 tips (beads add, supernatant/ethanol removal)
  rail35 pos2 = magnet + CellTreat_96_wellplate_350ul_Fb work plate, column 1
  rail35 pos3 = 12-well reservoir/trough

Reservoir map:
  A1 = NEBNext Sample Purification Beads
  A2 = 80% ethanol wash 1
  A3 = 80% ethanol wash 2
  A4 = Elution Buffer
  A12 = waste

post-ligation volumes (NEB #M7634 Section 3.4):
  beads add = 93.0 uL x8 (1.1X), p300
  supernatant remove = 180.0 uL x8, p300
  ethanol add/remove = 200.0/200.0 uL x8, p300 (x2 washes)
  residual ethanol remove = 20.0 uL x8, p50
  elution add = 29.0 uL x8, p50-low; keep 28.0 uL (off-deck transfer)

=== EM-seq post-ligation cleanup (1.1X) - all motions ===
Between beads-add and supernatant-remove: incubate 5 min RT, then let beads pellet on
the magnet (operator/timed; not modeled here). Same before elution.

P300 ADD: beads add: reservoir A1 -> mag col 1; 93.0 uL x8 (tip col 1)
Returning p300 tips...

P300 REMOVE: supernatant remove: mag col 1 -> waste A12; 180.0 uL x8 (tip col 1)
Returning p300 tips...

P300 ADD: ethanol wash 1 add: reservoir A2 -> mag col 1; 200.0 uL x8 (tip col 1)
Returning p300 tips...

P300 REMOVE: ethanol wash 1 remove: mag col 1 -> waste A12; 200.0 uL x8 (tip col 1)
Returning p300 tips...

P300 ADD: ethanol wash 2 add: reservoir A3 -> mag col 1; 200.0 uL x8 (tip col 1)
Returning p300 tips...

P300 REMOVE: ethanol wash 2 remove: mag col 1 -> waste A12; 200.0 uL x8 (tip col 1)
Returning p300 tips...

P50 RESIDUAL REMOVE: mag col 1 -> waste A12; 20.0 uL x8 (tip col 1)
Returning p50 tips...

Air-dry the beads 30 s - 2 min (operator/timed; do not over-dry). Then elute:

P50 LOW ADD: elution add: reservoir A4 -> mag col 1; 29.0 uL x8 (tip col 1)
Returning p50 tips...

SUCCESS: post-ligation cleanup motions completed. Eluate (29.0 uL) is on the
beads; transfer the clear 28.0 uL off the magnet to a fresh column (off-deck).
Stopping STAR backend...
Done.

